---
import ThemeLayout from '../layouts/ThemeLayout.astro';
---
<ThemeLayout page="services" heading="Manual Testing">

  <section class="inner-page padd-section">
    <div class="container">

      <div class="row align-items-center mb-5" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-12 text-center mb-4 mb-md-0">
          <div class="svc-hero-icon">
            <i class="fa fa-check-square-o"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-10">
          <h3>Comprehensive Quality Assurance by Expert Testers</h3>
          <p>Rayinfos Technologies quality assurance team adopts a comprehensive approach covering every aspect and feature of your product. Using the right combination of domain expertise, technology and cross-domain training, our team focuses on improving product quality while lowering costs.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i></div>
            <h5>Reduced Timeframe</h5>
            <p>Lowered test time frames with real-time tracking of activities so your product reaches release faster without shortcuts.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-check-circle"></i></div>
            <h5>Comprehensive Coverage</h5>
            <p>Complete confirmation of every feature using tools for defect management and manual testing for real-time activity tracking.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-star"></i></div>
            <h5>Better Test Quality</h5>
            <p>Technology-driven and industry-specific testing backed by cross-tool and cross-domain training provided to our workforce.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-dollar"></i></div>
            <h5>Cost Effective</h5>
            <p>Affordable manual testing services that lower costs without compromising on the thoroughness or quality of the test process.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-chrome"></i></div>
            <h5>Multi-browser Testing</h5>
            <p>Flexibility to test on multiple browsers and in various environments, ensuring consistent behaviour for all your users.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-flask"></i></div>
            <h5>Specialist Test Lab</h5>
            <p>A dedicated specialist test lab delivering the full range of quality assurance services with trained domain experts.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</ThemeLayout>
